name: Alicia
description: Alicia was found in a box when she was a puppy, she had been left at a dumpster. When she arrived at the shelter she was shy and had experienced trauma but has evolved to a happy social dog who loves cuddles and to play with her best firend Hanna at the shelter. She is the most precious dog you could find, book a meeting with Alicia to se for yourself.

name: Bert
description: Bert is the sweetest boy and loves to play with everybody and take naps in the sun. He loves to dig holes in the yard and to bite Alicia in the tail. Bert has no problem with children and would fit a family with children. He likes when things happens around him and is always there to see what's going on.

name: Hank
description: Hank is a lovely boy who has not been so lucky with life but still loves everybody and has lots of energi. He is starting to get a little bit old, he has lots of energy left but would fit someone with a big house and a backyard perfect so he can go out whenever he likes to.

name: Iris
description: Iris is a little diva who loves to prank all the animals on the shelter. She is a healthy little cat who loves to play with her toys and the other animals at the shelter. She likes to run freely around as an outdoor cat and is always back for a snack and to sleep.

name: Gustav
description: Gustav loves to sleep and eat. He is really like the character Gustav, therefore the name. He is a little grumpy and is most of his time by himself. He would love a home where he get all the attention and food for himself.

name: Oscar
description: Oscar is a gentleman who always has an eye on the female dogs. He loves cuddles but is getting old so he would really love to find a forever home where he can relax the rest of his time with lots of love and food.

name: Camilla
description: Camilla is a active dog who loves to go on long walks in the forrest, and she never says no to a play session.

name: Douglas
description: Douglas is a active dog who loves to run frealy in the yard, and she never says no to a play session.
health: Douglas has a problem with one of his legs.

name: Havana
description: Havana is a beautiful havana brown cat, she has the best personality and will always come to say hi.

name: Treo
description: Treo is a tricky one, he loves to play pranks on the dogs at the shelter and thinks he owns the place, but as soon he gets to know you he will not stop licking your face.

name: Neo
description: Neo is a prefect little guy, he always checks up on you and greets you hello. He will go for some adventures but is always comming back when he is hungry or down for a cuddle is the sofa.

name: Sully
description: Sully would fit a childrens family perfect, he loves when children comes by to say hi. He is the sweetest with everybody and loves to play with his favorite toy.

name: Sir
description: Sir loves his privacy but would really be in need of a forever home where he has some friends.

name: Petunia
description: Petunia loves to dig holes and eat carrots. She loves her best friend Sir and they always dig holes and sleep together.
